           CALL 'wui-start-html' USING wc-pagetitle

           *> decompose and save current post string
           CALL 'write-post-string' USING wn-rtn-code

           IF wn-rtn-code = ZERO
               PERFORM A0110-init-add-action
           END-IF

        .
